gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Button" data-key="button" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025564" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-gpicon-button" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709742025564"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-stretch-lg="0" data-stretch-sm="0" data-stretch-xs="0" data-stretch-md="1"><a class="button btn gf_button gf_gs-button-element gf_gs-button---large" href="https://rtrk.gartenpfad.com/click" target="_blank" data-scroll-speed="2000" data-exc="" data-scroll-speed-sm="2000" data-scroll-speed-xs="2000" data-scroll-speed-md="2000" aria-describedby="a11y-new-window-external-message" rel="null noopener"><span>VON GARTENPFLEGERN EMPFOHLEN ➡️</span></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025643" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1709742025643" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="color: rgb(109, 182, 68);">Vielseitig & Effektiv - Der Alleskönner&nbsp;</span></h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025614" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709742025614"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Ein vielseitiger Alleskönner hat die Bühne betreten, um jede Art von Verunreinigung zuverlässig zu beseitigen. Diese bahnbrechende Lösung verspricht eine saubere und gepflegte Umgebung, ohne den geringsten Aufwand. Die Montage gestaltet sich kinderleicht und erfordert keine komplizierten Installationen, sodass jeder sofort mit der Gartenpflege loslegen kann.</p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025519" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709742025519" data-resolution="480x480"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/1787cb4d-23ed-41b2-9b9e-a33e0d1e8097/-/format/auto/-/preview/480x480/-/quality/lighter/GEZOPtFERStahldraht_7_1.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="80%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="480" natural-height="480" width="480" height="480" loading="lazy"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025665" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709742025665"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Effizienz und Schnelligkeit stehen im Mittelpunkt dieses innovativen Gartenhelfers. Mit einer Leistung, die 150-mal stärker ist als bei herkömmlichen Trimmern, erzielt er mühelos und in kürzester Zeit makellose Ergebnisse.&nbsp;</p></div></div><div data-label="Button" data-key="button" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1712232980025" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-gpicon-button" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1712232980025"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-stretch-lg="0" data-stretch-sm="0" data-stretch-xs="0" data-stretch-md="1"><a class="button btn gf_button gf_gs-button-element gf_gs-button---large" href="https://rtrk.gartenpfad.com/click" target="_blank" data-scroll-speed="2000" data-exc="" data-scroll-speed-sm="2000" data-scroll-speed-xs="2000" data-scroll-speed-md="2000" aria-describedby="a11y-new-window-external-message" rel="null noopener"><span>Jetzt Rabatte und Verfügbarkeit prüfen ➡️</span></a></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025589" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1709742025589" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="color: rgb(109, 182, 68);">Super-effizientes Design für schnelle Ergebnisse</span></h2></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025604" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709742025604" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0736/4077/1889/files/GEZOPtFERStahldraht_4_1_3aff81a3-a706-44dc-914e-c119ba4ba827_3000x3000.jpg?v=1684747470" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="80%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1080" natural-height="1080" width="1080" height="1080" loading="lazy"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025595" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709742025595"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Die mühsame Arbeit des Unkrautjätens wird mit diesem Produkt im Handumdrehen zur Vergangenheit. Ein leistungsstarker Rasentrimmerkopf sorgt für ein makelloses Ergebnis und entfernt hartnäckiges Unkraut effektiv, während er gleichzeitig schonend zu den betroffenen Stellen ist.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025540" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1709742025540" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="color: rgb(109, 182, 68);">Passt auf 98% aller handelsüblichen Trimmer</span></h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025625" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709742025625"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--color-body); font-style: var(--font-style-body);">Eine der herausragenden Eigenschaften des ProfiTrims ist seine Kompatibilität mit allen Trimmern, einschließlich beliebter Marken wie Stihl, Gardena, Karcher, Bosch, Makita, Parkside, Worx und Einhell. Sie brauchen sich keine Gedanken über Montageprobleme oder den Kauf eines neuen Trimmers zu machen.</span><br></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025560" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709742025560" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0736/4077/1889/files/DesignohneTitel_3000x3000.jpg?v=1681304095" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="80%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1080" natural-height="1080" width="1080" height="1080" loading="lazy"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025572" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1709742025572" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="color: rgb(109, 182, 68);"><br></span></h2><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="color: rgb(109, 182, 68);">Kundenfragen beantwortet:&nbsp;</span></h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025576" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709742025576"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">A: Was macht den ProfiTrim von anderen Trimmern auf dem Markt unterscheidbar?<br></span>Dank der doppelten Versiegelung unserer Drahtbürste, halten die Borsten auch bei starker Beanspruchung sowie hoher Drehzahl und haben eine längere Lebensdauer als billige Konkurrenzprodukte.</p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-weight: 700;">B: Wie lange hält der ProfiTrim?</span></p><p>Der ProfiTrim ist 150 Mal stärker als konventionelle Trimmer, was bedeutet, dass er jahrelang halten kann, ohne ersetzt werden zu müssen.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">C: Kann der ProfiTrim von jedermann verwendet werden?</span></p><p>Der ProfiTrim ist benutzerfreundlich konzipiert und kann von jedermann verwendet werden, unabhängig von seinem Erfahrungs- oder Schulungsniveau.&nbsp;</p><p><span style="font-weight: bold; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--color-body); font-style: var(--font-style-body);"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: bold; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--color-body); font-style: var(--font-style-body);">D: Ist der ProfiTrim einfach zu installieren?</span></p><p>Unsere Unkrautfugenbürste lässt sich auf fast alle Unkrautschneider montieren.&nbsp;</p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025510" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1709742025510" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="color: rgb(109, 182, 68);">Das sagen begeisterte Gartenliebhaber!</span></h2></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1709742025590" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1709742025590" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1687954544687" data-id="1687954544687" style="min-height: 1px; display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025596" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709742025596" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-left-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://images.loox.io/uploads/2023/5/5/J9X7FPdwa_mid.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="1080" height="1440" data-width="350px" data-height="350px" title="" natural-width="1080" natural-height="1440" loading="lazy"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1687954557002" data-id="1687954557002" style="min-height: 1px; display: block; flex-direction: unset; justify-content: unset;"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709742025630" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709742025630" data-resolution="3000x3000">